Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:04.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這 這個我也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這張超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,簡直就是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱大人太不妙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這全都是心壽拍的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我超喜歡心壽拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:28.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我當初只是請她拍照而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果她就幫我創了我的COS名和帳號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:34.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為姊姊都不想給別人看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:44.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我想著 "想讓人看看姊姊可愛的照片"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就問姊姊能不能幫她辦帳號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:50.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後就有好多人按讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:50.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第一次投稿)\N然後就有好多人按讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(目前拍的裡面最喜歡的4張)\N然後就有好多人按讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(變成人魚了)\N然後就有好多人按讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很多人都稱讚了姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:02.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是不知道要怎麼回覆陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就全都忽視了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才沒和任何人有來往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是為了自我滿足才COS的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他人的評價怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追隨者也增加了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想說姊姊果然很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就覺得很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心壽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:25.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:29.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳超喜歡朱朱大人的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:32.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱大人很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少 少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,閃耀著璀璨色彩的重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:54.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不會忘記的 沒錯 就是這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在水平線的遙遠彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:09.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,流露的嘆息隨著波浪消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:14.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你找出了我隱藏的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:20.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,並牽起我的手向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:26.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,滿面笑容的你映入了眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:31.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,波浪濺起時的兩個身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:36.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,響起的腳步聲邁向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:43.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不斷追逐著陽光下赤腳的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:48.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,敞開心胸潑起了水花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:53.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爛漫搖曳的水面染上璀璨色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:59.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,初次相遇了這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:04.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真摯地注視著夢想的美麗雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:09.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想在你身旁相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Be myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第8話 我推薦逆光拍)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相機是向爸爸借的單眼相機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳爸爸是攝影師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 拍照只是他的興趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:30.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為這是不用換鏡頭的相機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鏡頭是需要換的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以依照喜好更換喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(魚眼 標準 望遠)\N只要交換鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(魚眼 標準 望遠)\N即便是相同的角度拍也會有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(魚眼 標準 望遠)\N很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:42.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學 請說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和用手機拍攝還是差很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為畫質還是比較高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能做到的表現比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如像是以花為背景拍攝時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就可以用散景強調COSER本身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓前景的部分失焦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拍出有溫柔氛圍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要調整快門速度的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也可以清楚的拍下飄落的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺很有趣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:14.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順利拍出自己想要的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或是拍下意外的好表情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會想要拍得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拍出更可愛的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且拍的是朱朱大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是讓人有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說心壽不COS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:39.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看著別人COS不會也想COS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起來超可愛 很開心不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想說"我也想要"之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心壽也想COS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不會想COS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡拍姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心壽 可以讓我摸一下相機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相機真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想拍出漂亮的散景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要存錢 絕對要買!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,單眼相機大概要多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:20.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(鏡頭另售)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鏡頭另售!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:32.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太大聲了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果要買腳架和閃光燈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要更多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學都目瞪口呆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家在之前的活動裡拿著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然是這麼昂貴的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是不妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之在存到錢之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是先用手機拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學毫不猶豫地決定要買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相機的有很多種 價差很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,選個預算內的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-謝謝惠顧 -我們要去場勘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們也要一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為是第一次租攝影棚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以覺得先去看看比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:14.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我絕對要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請務必讓我們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那週末在新三鄉站會合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們要去的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,廢棄醫院攝影棚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來還有這種攝影棚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次到廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常期待今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上都睡不太著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這種感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-比想像得更陰暗呢 -和輸給公主雛菊的右直拳時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逃進的廢棄醫院一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然是很灰暗的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我很喜歡紫苑輸掉後自問自答的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說你真的全都看完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學 我們去上面看看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,走吧 心壽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-好的 -真是有氣氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾同學該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不擅長應付這種地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來不擅長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是不是反而太暗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為有閃光燈所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,簡直無敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:52.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,閃光燈和反光板也能用在戶外的攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有買的話比較方便喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算外面是晴天也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:55.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天氣好的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會因為太亮而睜不開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以要逆光拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肌膚的質感看起來也會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:13.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但這樣的話臉就會變暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才要用反光板打光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,假髮也會透光變得閃閃發亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,光澤也會變得更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那超棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也告訴五条同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很推薦逆光拍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想在拍起來好看的地方拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說心壽妳們去外拍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都去哪裡拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們家的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 沒事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是有點累而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起來不像沒事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳要回去入口等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好不容易能出黑百合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要好好確認裡面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不然就沒辦法拍出好照片不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會確認好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請在入口等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 我要自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是妳在勉強自己對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有將來的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:41.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想成為娃娃的頭師…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,製作娃娃臉部的工匠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是個很棒的夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,絕對要實現喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我曾夢想成為魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既厲害又閃閃發光的很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,穿著蓬蓬的可愛衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小時候就很憧憬著魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看得非常著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,認真地想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"我長大之後要成為魔法少女"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是上了小學就知道了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那全都是創造出來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便像魔法少女一樣努力 祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的夢想也是永遠不會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是升上國中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我發現有在賣魔法少女的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為沒有相關知識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連假髮要修整都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也沒有化妝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服裝的尺寸也不合身鬆垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然第一次的COS不堪入目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:07.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便如此我還是由衷地感到開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算全都是創作出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還是想實現我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明是那麼重要的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼要委託我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有很多比我更厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然事到如今 應該去委託其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼要委託我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:38.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我看到喜多川海夢她的照片時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嫉妒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也知道嫉妒什麼的很不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但真的羨慕到難以自制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想著"我也想穿這個人做的服裝"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"非這個人做的衣服不行"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的確有很多會做服裝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也無法好好說明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,講不出個所以然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我一定是在那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對你做的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對自己會嫉妒也很驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:27.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但人不會對不在乎的東西嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個女兒節娃娃是爺爺們做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是世界上最漂亮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界上最漂亮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是爺爺為了讓客人在眾多的娃娃店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,眼睛為之一亮而停下目光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:58.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜歡到覺得"這個娃娃是最棒的"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而拚了命做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你能說是最美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:05.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,停下目光是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是讓人一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等我長大之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想變得會做娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想變得像爺爺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:36.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新菜只要練習也能變得像爺爺一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等…怎麼了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼你在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:50.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:51.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常感謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我現在終於知道那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺有多開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了有一天能被那麼稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-一定會… -乾紗壽葉 17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就讀女子完全中學的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被年齡相仿的異性握住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-五条同學 雷超大聲的 你們沒事吧 -怎麼了嗎 乾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-五条同學 雷超大聲的 你們沒事吧 -妳沒事吧 乾同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了 考完了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為海水浴場還沒開放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全沒有人超棒的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,簡直就像是包場一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天是來拍照的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場勘的時候說了想要逆光拍攝對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在拍起來好看的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 完全沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,期末考不是考完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在不是7月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正值夏天對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:33.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,穿著制服來海邊玩不是很青春嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:41.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學就是這種人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何等行動力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學 也給我些薯條
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,薯條 薯條
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的漢堡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還在跟著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去遠一點的地方吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 都難得來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不就會想邊看海邊喝珍奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且連野餐墊都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又被搶走的時候再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,薯條就放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,趁現在離遠一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,漢堡還剩下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不小心就亂丟垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老鷹先生再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是五条同學的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超級好吃的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,漢堡和魩仔魚真搭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,珍奶真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學要喝一口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用了 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,海風吹起來好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下去海裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幫我拿這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,踩踩水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為一時興起所以也沒帶泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是隨興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你看 超大的海帶芽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有在看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超級棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,海浪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,腳漸漸沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也太吃驚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是第一次來海邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,騙人的吧? 真假?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說起來埼玉也沒有海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我從小時候就只顧著看娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:29.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學爺爺練習畫臉覺得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一直沉浸在練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有把其他事物放在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以有很多沒去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:47.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之前爺爺叫我要多看看其他東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和電視還有照片上看到的完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大海真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那和我一起去各式各樣的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬 馬上就是暑假對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…會一直約你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兩 兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請妳多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:39.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好像有些口渴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我去喝點茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:42.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:53.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順 順勢就說了要兩個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙 不妙 超不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是被發現臉紅的話好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好害羞 好害羞 好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣暑假能一直見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全身 全身都是海帶芽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,黏答答 黏答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:52.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我 我想走進更深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果就踩到海帶芽跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要怎麼回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會乾的 會乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:04.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,U FU FU FU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不經意地發現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定是陷入了戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為命運的作弄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:34.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對那一句話怦然心動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:40.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不能再更期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在兩人追尋著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:50.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一心一意純潔的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:53.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,漸漸動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:57.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好 不小心就對你一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:00.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太喜歡你了 該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,坦率面對自己內心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以啊 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:15.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在身旁看著含苞待放的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,NANANA NANANA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,U FU FU FU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第9話)\N(看了照片之後發生了些事)